<h1 id="introduction">Introduction</h1>

<p><a href="https://curl.haxx.se/">curl</a> is a command/library(libcurl) available on most Unix-based systems. It is used as an abbreviation for “Client URL”. It is used for several purposes such as: navigation, data insertion via the web, download, data transfer and among others. It supports several protocols.</p>

<!-- QUADRADO -->
<script async="" src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

