<h1 id="tip-4-download-the-file-saving-with-a-name-you-defined">Tip 4. Download the file saving with a name you defined:</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl givingsoup.org/downloads/distro.iso <span class="nt">-o</span> mydistro.iso</code></pre></figure>

<h1 id="tip-5-resume-an-interrupted-download">Tip 5. Resume an interrupted download</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl <span class="nt">-C</span> - <span class="nt">-O</span> http://givingsoup.org/downloads/distro.iso</code></pre></figure>

