<h1 id="tip-6-download-multiple-files">Tip 6. Download multiple files</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl <span class="nt">-O</span> http://yoursite.com/mydistro.iso <span class="nt">-O</span> http://givingsoup.org/downloads/data.txt</code></pre></figure>

<h1 id="tip-7-download-urls-from-a-file">Tip 7. Download URLs from a file</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">cat </span>urls.txt
givingsoup.org/downloads/distro.iso
givingsoup.org/downloads/data.txt
xargs <span class="nt">-n</span> 1 curl <span class="nt">-O</span> &lt; urls.txt</code></pre></figure>

