<h1 id="tip-8-limit-download-speed">Tip 8. Limit download speed</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl <span class="nt">--limit-rate</span> 100K http://givingsoup.org/downloads/distro.iso <span class="nt">-O</span></code></pre></figure>

<h1 id="tip-9-download-with-progress-bar">Tip 9. Download with progress bar</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl -# <span class="nt">-O</span> givingsoup.org/downloads/distro.iso</code></pre></figure>

<h1 id="tip-10-query-http-headers">Tip 10. Query HTTP headers</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl <span class="nt">-I</span> en.terminalroot.com.br</code></pre></figure>

<blockquote>
  <p>Not all sites allow this query.</p>
</blockquote>

<h1 id="tip-11-specify-a-user-agent">Tip 11. Specify a User Agent</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl https://gnu.terminalroot.com.br/ip.php
<span class="c"># Example Windows 10 Edge:</span>
curl http://localhost <span class="nt">--user-agent</span> <span class="s2">"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/64.0.3282.140 Safari/537.36 Edge/17.17134"</span></code></pre></figure>

