<h1 id="tip-12-apache-authentication">Tip 12. Apache authentication</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl <span class="nt">-u</span> user:pass <span class="nt">-O</span> http://givingsoup.org/m/secret/my-secret-files.tar.gz</code></pre></figure>

